# ClaudeBox Squad Configuration File
#
# Format: branch:profile:description
# 
# - branch: Git branch name (will be created if it doesn't exist)
# - profile: ClaudeBox profile(s) to use (comma-separated, optional)
# - description: Human-readable task description (optional)
#
# Lines starting with # are comments
# Empty lines are ignored
#
# Example configurations:

# Feature development with different profiles
feature/auth:python:Add OAuth2 authentication
feature/api:node:Build REST API endpoints
feature/ui:node:Create React frontend components

# Bug fixes
bugfix/validation:python:Fix input validation errors
bugfix/performance:python,node:Optimize database queries

# Multiple tasks on same codebase
refactor/models:python:Refactor database models
refactor/tests:python:Update test suite

# Experimental features
experiment/ml-integration:python:Integrate machine learning model
experiment/graphql:node:Add GraphQL support

# Documentation work
docs/api-reference::Update API documentation
docs/user-guide::Write user guide

# Simple examples (no profile specified, uses default)
feature/simple-fix::Quick bug fix
feature/another-task::Another task

# Advanced: Multiple profiles
feature/fullstack:python,node,rust:Full-stack feature with multiple languages
